['k = int(input())
# print(b, k)
i=0
while i<k:
    a = int(input())
    b=  list(map(int,input().split(" ")))
    b.sort(reverse=True)
    base1=b[0]
    base2=b[1]
    # print(b)
    # print(base1,base2)

    ans=0
    index=2
    while index<len(b) and ans<=base2+2 and b[index]>base2:
        ans=ans+1
        index=index+1

    print(min((len(b)-2)-ans,base2-1))


    i=i+1']
